2026-03-19 20:16:06 | INFO     | chatbi.core.llm_client:_parse_response:246 -       参数: {"code": "\n# 更详细的分析\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"趋势分析\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\n\n# 月度汇总\nmonthly_summary = df.groupby('month').agg({\n    'product_a_sales': 'sum',\n    'product_b_sales': 'sum',\n    'product_c_sales': 'sum',\n    'total_sales': 'sum',\n    'total_quantity': 'sum'\n}).reset_index()\n\nprint(\"\\n【月度销售汇总】\")\nprint(monthly_summary.to_string(index=False))\n\n# 计算同比增长\nmonthly_summary['sales_growth'] = monthly_summary['total_sales'].pct_change() * 100\nprint(\"\\n\\n【月销售同比增长率】\")\nfor i, row in monthly_summary.iterrows():\n    if i == 0:\n        print(f\"  {row['month']}: 基期数据\")\n    else:\n        print(f\"  {row['month']}: {row['sales_growth']:+.1f}%\")\n\n# 周期性分析\ndf['day_of_week'] = df['date'].dt.day_name()\ndf['weekday_num'] = df['date'].dt.weekday\n\nprint(\"\\n\\n【周期性分析 - 平均日销售额】\")\nweekday_avg = df.groupby('day_of_week')['total_sales'].mean().reindex([\n    'Monday', 'Tuesday', 'Wednesday', 'Thursday', 'Friday', 'Saturday', 'Sunday'\n])\nfor day, avg in weekday_avg.items():\n    day_cn = {'Monday': '周一', 'Tuesday': '周二', 'Wednesday': '周三', \n              'Thursday': '周四', 'Friday': '周五', 'Saturday': '周六', 'Sunday': '周日'}[day]\n    print(f\"  {day_cn}: {avg:.1f} 元\")\n\n# 找出销售最好和最差的日子\nbest_day = df.loc[df['total_sales'].idxmax()]\nworst_day = df.loc[df['total_sales'].idxmin()]\n\nprint(\"\\n\\n【极值分析】\")\nprint(f\"  销售最高日: {best_day['date'].strftime('%Y-%m-%d')} - {best_day['total_sales']} 元\")\nprint(f\"  销售最低日: {worst_day['date'].strftime('%Y-%m-%d')} - {worst_day['total_sales']} 元\")\n\n# 相关性分析\nprint(\"\\n\\n【各产品销售额相关性】\")\ncorr_matrix = df[['product_a_sales', 'product_b_sales', 'product_c_sales']].corr()\nprint(corr_matrix.round(3))\n"}
